#: ../../I/intertwingled.rst:5
msgid "intertwingled"
msgstr "intertwingled"

#: ../../I/intertwingled.rst:7
msgid ""
"adj. [Invented by Theodor Holm Nelson, prob. a blend of \"mingled\" and "
"\"intertwined\".] Connected together in a complex way; specifically, "
"composed of one another's components."
msgstr ""
"形容詞。[Theodor Holm Nelsonによる造語。おそらく「mingled」と「intertwined」の混成語。] "
"複雑な仕方でつなぎ合わされていること。具体的には、互いの構成要素から成っていること。"
